# =========================
*.md
!apps/web/src/contents/**/*.md
!apps/web/src/contents/posts/**/*.md
!apps/web/src/contents/portfolios/**/*.md
!packages/ui/src/**/*.md
LICENSE
CONTRIBUTING.md

